│ ~1 row                                           │
╰─────────────────────────┬────────────────────────╯
╭─ IRESEARCH_SCAN ────────┴────────────────────────╮
│ Index: tp_idx                                    │
│ Filter:                                          │
│ ╭─ And ───────────────╮                          │
│ ╰──────────┬──────────╯                          │
│            ├────────────────────────╮            │
│ ╭─ Starts With ───────╮  ╭─ Automaton ─────────╮ │
│ │ Field: body(string) │  │ Field: body(string) │ │
│ │ Prefix: a           │  │ Pattern: a.*e       │ │
│ │ Limit: 1024         │  ╰─────────────────────╯ │
│ ╰─────────────────────╯                          │
│ TsDict: body                                     │
│ Projections:                                     │
│ sdb_inverted_index_term$body                     │
│ ~1 row                                           │
╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────╯

query T
SELECT unnest(ts_dict_agg(cat)) AS term
FROM tp_idx WHERE cat LIKE 'a%' AND cat BETWEEN 'ap' AND 'az' ORDER BY term
----
term
apple
apricot
avocado

query
EXPLAIN SELECT unnest(ts_dict_agg(cat)) AS term
FROM tp_idx WHERE cat LIKE 'a%' AND cat BETWEEN 'ap' AND 'az'
----
